Class SimpleInterval

java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Object>
public class SimpleInterval
extends Domain

Represents intervals of time described by a start and an end time. Used as a domain for the APSPSolver variables (i.e., TimePoints), and also as a utility class to represent intervals (e.g., for constraints, etc.). Derived from original implementation by the Planning and Scheduling Team (ISTC-CNR) under project APSI.

Author:
Federico Pecora and Planning and Scheduling Team
